    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place" rend="center">Department of Justice</name>
                    <name type="place" rend="right"><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></name>.
                    <date when="1871-05-13" rend="right">May 13, <hi rend="italic">18</hi>71</date>.
                </dateline>
                <salute>Mrs. Botta,</salute>
                <salute>My dear Madam,</salute><ptr target="yal.00105_n1"/>
            </opener>

            <p>In answer to your request of some days since, I send you the MS. of a small piece I have written, to be printed forthwith in the June Galaxy.<ptr target="yal.00105_n2"/></p>
            
            <p>According to your request, I also send a picture.</p>
            
            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
